text: Joseph H. Gaskill (May 23, 1851 – November 25, 1935) was a judge on the New Jersey Court of Common Pleas and Justice of the New Jersey Supreme Court from 1893 to 1896. HI son Thomas L. Gaskill was also a lawyer.http://www.history.njd.uscourts.gov/judges/bank_bios/Thomas_L_Gaskill Gaskill was a native of Mount Holly and later resided in Moorestown.
